    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Hanguana sitinurbayai Randi.A–B. Plant habit in situ. C. Habit of single plant. D. Indumentum on abaxial leaf surface. E–F. Lamina, adaxial and abaxial surface. All photos by A. Randi from type specimen." ;
